Web Description:
Spare Adaptor cones to allow Spin Doctor front hub to change from; 
9x100mm spaced QR fitting 
to; 
20x110mm Through Axle type use.

20mm T-axle cones. 
Blk CNC alloy. Pr.

Note - these are replacement spares - as the Spin Doctor hub inc. these items when purchased new.

Note: There are 2 types... ;
Mk1 (earlier hubs) have offset bearings with 2 different sized spacers: Disc Side: 28mm & Non-Disc side: 18mm) 

Mk2 (later - mid 2006 onwards) are more equally spaced. Disc side: 16mm deep, Non-Disc side: 18mm deep.

